text: Dainty may refer to: * 9758 Dainty, asteroid * HMS Dainty, four ships of the Royal Navy * Dainty, a street ball game played in Schnitzelburg, Louisville == People with the surname == * Bert Dainty (1879–1961), an English footballer and manager * Billy Dainty (1927–1986), a British comedian * Christopher Dainty, American physicist * Harold Dainty (1892–1961), an English cricketer == See also == *
